    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine, untouched interior, this motorcar offers an unrivaled ownership experience for the most discerning enthusiast. A rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such distinguished caliber.",
      "price": 48500.0,
