    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerhouse utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver linear, naturally aspirated power. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a functional M-Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, showing no signs of subframe fatigue or floor-pan stress. Suspension geometry is factory-perfect, riding on staggered forged Style 67 wheels. This specimen boasts original paint depth across all panels and a pristine interior, representing a pinnacle of early-2000s German engineering and mechanical purity.",
